PrecisRe-appointment of LOIS DELIA FIGG, of Toronto, Ontario, as a full-time member of the Convention Refugee Determination Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Toronto Regional Office), to hold office during good behaviour for a term of five years; and designation of LOIS DELIA FIGG as a coordinating member of the Convention Refugee Determination Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Toronto Regional Office), for a term ending April 23, 2004; effective June 26, 2002.
